name: Failentine Bouquete Cake
description:
Roses are red, violets are blue. She says “Thanks, you are too kind”, now your broken heart needs a cure. Worry not, we prepared this bouquet cake to full of sweetness to cheers you.

It consists of vanilla cake with smooth cream and blueberry jelly inside. It is surrounded by wavy chocolate coated with gold leaf as the accent and decorated with rose buttercream and meringue kisses.

We only serve it for 20 pieces of a whole cake. Grab yours!
